{"tid":1946224,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政府修例禁四人以上聚會 婚禮喪禮等可豁免 真奇怪啊","createTime":"2020-03-27T13:02:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T13:45:41.000Z","uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f6757718ecbbdc6ffe2a6dd1b97eb539cd5dc297","tid":1946224,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:02:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=385838&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D385838%26refer%3DShare&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fv8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=b8f2408a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D385838%26refer%3DShare&h=2005b26c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=385838&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"4053b28a7ef727c726b2f18f43417d067a680a5f","tid":1946224,"uid":125193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:03:53.000Z","msg":"港聞<br />\n政府修例禁四人以上聚會 婚禮喪禮等可豁免<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】行政長官林鄭月娥宣布，因應疫情嚴峻，行政會議通過修例，禁止四人以上在公眾地方聚會，但工作間、婚禮喪禮等可豁免，<strong>將於周日零時起生效十四天。違例者定額罰款2000元，或最高罰款25000元、監禁六個月。</strong><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥說：「<strong>簡單而言，多於四人聚集便會被禁止，是違法；但大家可以想象，日常生活及城市運作有很多聚會是多於四人，所以規例提供了一系列豁免群組聚集，大概有十二項獲豁免群組聚集</strong>，即多於四人仍可聚集的活動，包括工作間的聚集，包括履行政府功能，如同今天多於四人，這裏更多人，所以我們正在履行政府功能，亦包括法庭、立法會、區議會程序，即這些法定機構的工作及會議可以繼續進行，亦包括喪禮及婚禮。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bca8e66d0c04f248ffe79ef8b9e2c2e9ac73061","tid":1946224,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:09:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20faed0c0024d318836e02a8c57a726850510268","tid":1946224,"uid":280412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:13:49.000Z","msg":"坐監都係聚會<br />\n應該要禁罰監禁"},{"pid":"8fbc46d45dd177c4c866161ff152d1502b54a80e","tid":1946224,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:34:34.000Z","msg":"集會可以用網上<br />\n冇人出剩係得手足會好大獲"},{"pid":"bbd52e22d1975c0ab1441960b2f3d59ed8f9ee10","tid":1946224,"uid":272030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T13:45:41.000Z","msg":"黑警一個人都可以告你非法集結 仲洗4個人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}